  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom apartments</strong> are around 35-40m² sleeping two to four people. These apartments have one twin bedroom and a sofa bed in the lounge</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments</strong>  are around 55-65m² sleeping four to six people. These apartments have a double bedroom, one twin bedroom and a sofa bed in the lounge. They also have an extra shower room and separate toilet. These apartments may be duplex.</p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments</strong> are around 70-80m² sleeping six to eight people. These apartments have one double bedroom, two twin bedrooms and a sofa bed in the lounge. They also have extra shower room and separate toilet. These apartments may be duplex.</p>
<p><span>Beds are made on arrival, except beds in the living room and end of stay cleaning (excluding the kitchen) is included. </span><span>One linen set with towels is included per person, per week. </span><span>A complete clean can be arranged through the reception for a local fee. Maximum occupancy includes babies and children. </span><span></span></p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Wi-Fi</span></li>
<li><span>Balcony or terrace</span></li>
<li><span>Satellite TV</span></li>
<li><span>Fully equipped kitchen with ceramic hobs, microwave, oven, fridge, dishwasher, coffee machine, kettle, blender and </span>toaster</li>
<li>Nespresso coffee machine</li>
<li>Condiment kit</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li><span>Cleaning kit</span></li>
<li><span>Bathroom with WC</span></li>
<li><span>Hairdryer</span></li>
<li><span>Toiletries</span></li>
<li><span>Bathrobe and slippers</span></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
